Title: Anonymous Communication and Anonymous  
Author: Cash Daniel R. Simon 
Address: One Microsoft Way Redmond WA 98052 USA  
Affiliation: Microsoft Corp.  
Abstract: We propose considering the problem of electronic cash in the context of a network in which anonymous, untraceable communication is assumed to be possible. We present a formal model for such a network, and define security criteria for an electronic cash system in such a setting. Finally, we show that there exists a remarkably simple electronic cash system which meets the security criteria of the proposed model. Key words: Electronic cash, anonymous communication 
